Package com.indooratlas.android

com.indooratlas.android contains interfaces of the IndoorAtlas Android API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CalibrationState
    CalibrationState interface provides access to a status event conveying momentary state of the calibration.
    FutureResult<R>
    Result of asynchronous computation.
    GeoPoint
    GeoPoint interface provides the position estimate in the WGS 84 coordinate system.
    ImagePoint
    ImagePoint interface provides the position estimate in the coordinate system of the image that was used in mapping.
    IndoorAtlas
    Main entry point for interacting with IndoorAtlas positioning services.
    IndoorAtlasListener
    IndoorAtlasListener is the public callback interface of IndoorAtlas API.
    MetricPoint
    MetricPoint interface provides x and y coordinates of the position estimate in meters.
    ProgressCallback  
    ResultCallback<R>  
    ServiceState
    ServiceState encapsulates the response from IndoorAtlas.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorCodes
    ErrorCodes class contains the error codes used in service failures.
    FloorPlan
    Represents floor plan data received from server.
    IndoorAtlasFactory  
    PositionerParameters
    PositionerParameters is a class for passing positioning parameters to IndoorAtlas.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CalibrationEvent
    CalibrationEvent specifies the types of calibration events.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IndoorAtlasException
    IndoorAtlasException wraps exceptions thrown by the IndoorAtlas API.

Package com.indooratlas.android Description

com.indooratlas.android contains interfaces of the IndoorAtlas Android API.
